  "elapsed_s": 95.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he somehow smelled out that we are from the-- and the front was outside.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The front we heard-- we heard the-- the-- the shooting from outside.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He said, oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] While he-- So then he says, excuse-- he went out, he said, excuse me, I have to do this and this.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I says to him, I don't like it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I just don't like it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was in the-- late in the evening.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Going-- going a little further, we saw that he's coming back with a [POLISH], a police, you know, to get us out, a Polack.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we took the way, the road, and we went to the village of Chrzanow, Chrzanow On the way to Chrzanow, there's [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] and [INAUDIBLE] was-- was-- was known to what it-- it was a-- a manufacturer of shoes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was known, like here Florsheim.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But there was the [INAUDIBLE] and the next-- next little village was Libiaz, also.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we had customers in Libiaz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we-- while we walked this forest, we saw already there something which was-- it wasn't-- it wasn't like it's supposed to be.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We saw barrels of sand from both sides.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody walks-- no-- no-- no-- no man's land.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By the end-- by the-- by the end of the road coming into Libiaz there, we were stopped.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Where are you going?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What is this here?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This-- this is-- this was-- this was forbidden to walk there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we found out there was a Howitzer-- you know a Howitzer, a-- a-- a cannon.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By the end of the road was a cannon and there's the front there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I just came into the front.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
